If any man should disagree with this,

1088
01:32:18,299 --> 01:32:20,130
let him speak now.

1089
01:32:28,609 --> 01:32:30,907
We have all sinned.

1090
01:32:30,978 --> 01:32:34,311
And we shall all suffer.

1091
01:32:36,317 --> 01:32:38,182
So let us now devote ourself

1092
01:32:38,252 --> 01:32:41,278
to the worship of the Lord our God,

1093
01:32:41,355 --> 01:32:45,689
in the hope of redeeming
ourselves in His eyes.

1094
01:32:48,896 --> 01:32:51,592
As for the psychiatrist,

1095
01:32:51,666 --> 01:32:53,861
it was her own stubbornness

1096
01:32:53,935 --> 01:32:56,995
and refusal to listen to reason

1097
01:32:57,071 --> 01:33:00,472
which brought her to tragedy.

1098
01:33:00,541 --> 01:33:03,408
Suffice to say

1099
01:33:03,477 --> 01:33:08,107
she left us without word
of her destination.

1100
01:33:56,530 --> 01:33:59,431
No.
[gasps]

1101
01:33:59,500 --> 01:34:02,594
No. It's not possible.

1102
01:34:05,306 --> 01:34:06,238
I'm dead?

1103
01:34:06,307 --> 01:34:07,467
I'm so sorry, Jane.

1104
01:34:09,844 --> 01:34:12,176
It's all my fault.

1105
01:34:12,246 --> 01:34:14,407
I should've stopped you
from going on that damned island.

1106
01:34:14,482 --> 01:34:15,471
I feel so guilty.

1107
01:34:15,549 --> 01:34:17,210
Don't say that.
[sniffles]

1108
01:34:18,352 --> 01:34:20,445
I'm happy you sent me.

1109
01:34:22,523 --> 01:34:25,788
I couldn't save David, you see.

1110
01:34:25,860 --> 01:34:27,452
But at least I saved Dorothy.

1111
01:34:27,528 --> 01:34:29,291
[sniffles]

1112
01:34:29,363 --> 01:34:31,331
I saved her, didn't I?

1113
01:34:32,867 --> 01:34:34,596
You saved her.

1114
01:34:36,537 --> 01:34:37,799
You brought her back to me.

1115
01:34:40,374 --> 01:34:41,398
She'll be acquitted,

1116
01:34:41,475 --> 01:34:44,444
and she'll stay here
until she's cured.

1117
01:34:47,715 --> 01:34:49,239
Yeah.

1118
01:34:53,054 --> 01:34:54,817
And now it's up to you, Jane.

1119
01:34:55,990 --> 01:34:59,619
You have to leave Dorothy's body.

1120
01:34:59,694 --> 01:35:02,219
She won't be free until you're gone.

1121
01:35:12,239 --> 01:35:14,764
Will you take good care of her?

1122
01:35:14,842 --> 01:35:16,537
I promise.

1123
01:35:29,523 --> 01:35:32,617
Keep it.
[sniffles]

1124
01:35:32,693 --> 01:35:34,684
David loved you so much.

1125
01:35:38,032 --> 01:35:39,556
I'll keep it forever.

1126
01:35:43,537 --> 01:35:47,268
Good-bye, my love.

1127
01:35:50,277 --> 01:35:51,904
[exhales]

1128
01:35:59,220 --> 01:36:01,313
[beeping]

1129
01:36:18,739 --> 01:36:19,933
